tags.description: Access Sidewalk to Fox Elementary from Camelot Villa connecting Millstone to Camelot Blvd

Homeowner installed fence/stone pavers to cut down on the mud; part of the brick fence was also removed allowing access to Hall Road via parking lots.  It's unpaved and requires a decent bike to navigate.

tags.note: Sidewalk paved/connected to remaining side-walk in July 2020.
